OME-Api version 0.01
====================

OME-Api is a perl module which uses the Java OMERO
code base to access the database. 

USAGE

You will need to have a working OMERO installation
to use this module. If running client-server (only 
option at the moment), then start tomcat and set the
CLASSPATH environment variable by sourcing:

  - components/client/target/Classpath.sh

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Inline
  Inline::Java

